						<div class="postbody">How do you typically place your start menu in your code? My start menu is just your typical 'Press Start' so I figured I would just put a small loop at the beginning that ends when the user presses start and from then on, the real code is done unless of course the game ends in which case it all just jumps back to that loop.
<br />
<br />What are the negatives to this approach?</div>

